# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:101
msgid "Aspect Ratio"
msgstr "Omjer stranica"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:101
msgid ""
"The aspect ratio of the final exported video. 1920×1080 reduces to 16:9. "
"This also takes into account the pixel ratio, for example 2:1 rectangular "
"pixels will affect the aspect ratio."
msgstr ""
"Omjer stranica konačnog izvezenog videa. 1920×1080 se svodi na 16:9. Također "
"uzima u obzir omjer piksela, na primjer, pravokutni pikseli 2:1 utječu na "
"omjer stranica."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:102
msgid "Pixel Ratio"
msgstr "Omjer piksela"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:102
msgid ""
"The ratio representing pixel shape. Most video profiles use a 1:1 square "
"pixel shape, but others will use rectangular pixels."
msgstr ""
"Omjer koji predstavlja oblik piksela. Većina video profila koristi kvadratne "
"piksele 1:1, ali neki koriste pravokutne piksele."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:103
msgid "Frame Rate"
msgstr "Brzina sličica"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:103
msgid "The frequency that the frames will be displayed at."
msgstr "Učestalost prikaza sličica."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:104
msgid "Interlaced"
msgstr "Naizmjenično"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:104
msgid ""
"Is this format used on alternating scan lines (i.e. broadcast and analog "
"formats)"
msgstr ""
"Koristi li se ovaj format na naizmjeničnim linijama skeniranja (npr. "
"emitiranje i analogni formati)"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:105
msgid "Spherical"
msgstr "Sferično"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../export.rst:105
msgid ""
"When enabled, injects spherical 360° metadata (SV3D atom) into the exported "
"file so compatible players immediately recognize it as a 360° video."
msgstr ""
"Kada je omogućeno, umeće sferične 360° metapodatke (SV3D atom) u izvezenu "
"datoteku kako bi ih kompatibilni reproduktori odmah prepoznali kao 360° "
"video."

